INSERT INTO `help` VALUES ('/questions.php','<p>\r\n<strong>The Questions function in WASSAIL</strong> allows the user to input and store pre-test, post-test, survey and one-shot questions and answers in the WASSAIL database. Once questions have been entered into the database, they can be compiled into templates that are the actual pre-test, post-test, survey and one-shot questionnaires administered during various classes, and throughout different academic years. Once a question has been attached to a template, that template can have the questionnaire responses added, allowing the user to generate various reports and gains analyses. An individual question can be used in a single template or in many templates. To avoid entering duplicate questions, the <em>Questions</em> function allows the user to print all questions for an accessible reference list of questions already entered into WASSAIL. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium\">1. From the WASSAIL main page select the Questions tab and then click on the &quot;add a new question&quot; bullet.\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" /><img src=\"include/helpimages/adding%20questions%20-%20W3-main.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"940\" height=\"163\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/adding%20new%20questions%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1029\" height=\"163\" align=\"right\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium\">\r\n2. Compose a question\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	a. Select the answer type that addresses your question by selecting the appropriate radio button.\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp; <img src=\"include/helpimages/choosing%20question%20type%20-%20W3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"938\" height=\"492\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	b.Select the <strong>Text </strong>tab to enter the text of your question.\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. Graphics may be added to the question by selecting the graphics widget&nbsp; <img src=\"file:///C:/DOCUME%7E1/wharder/LOCALS%7E1/Temp/moz-screenshot-6.png\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"file:///C:/DOCUME%7E1/wharder/LOCALS%7E1/Temp/moz-screenshot-7.png\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"include/helpimages/graphics%20widget%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"23\" height=\"23\" />\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			1. Insert the home location of the graphic\'s URL into the &quot;Image URL&quot; field\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			2. Tab down and click &quot;Insert&quot;\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		ii. The question layout may be previewed by selecting the preview widget&nbsp; <img src=\"include/helpimages/preview%20widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"23\" height=\"23\" />\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			1. HTML code may viewed\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			2. Hyperlinks may be created by highlighting text and clicking the hyperlink widget <img src=\"include/helpimages/hyperlink%20widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"26\" height=\"18\" />\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/adding%20text%20-%20W3-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1098\" height=\"394\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	c. Select the <strong>Categories</strong> tab to choose a WASSAIL-defined category. <strong>Categories</strong> enable controlled vocabulary classification according to question content. \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/adding%20categories%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1177\" height=\"483\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;d. Select the <strong>Tags</strong> tab to mark questions with a user-defined tag.<em> </em><strong>Tags</strong> enable natural language, folksonomic classification.\r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<p>\r\n		i. Adding ACRL Standards as a <strong>Tag</strong> to a question:\r\n		</p>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			<p>\r\n			1. Assigning <strong>Tags</strong> to a question can allow for corresponding ACRL Information Literacy Standards to be entered as a reference number for questions entered into WASSAIL. For consistency it is best to use a standard reference number in these cases. For example, ACRL2.3 would be used as the standard reference number for Standard Two, Performance Indicator 3. \r\n			</p>\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/adding%20tags%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1096\" height=\"372\" align=\"right\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	e. Select the <strong>Answers</strong> tab to provide answer selections for questions.\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. Answers for quantitative questions:\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/adding%20answers%20-%20W3-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1104\" height=\"527\" align=\"right\" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp; <img src=\"include/helpimages/chosing%20answers%20-%20FE.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1187\" height=\"524\" align=\"right\" /><br />\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n	&nbsp; <br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/deleting%20answers%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"876\" height=\"524\" align=\"right\" /> <br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		ii. Answers for qualitative questions\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			1. &quot;Opt out&quot; check-box: WASSAIL allows creation of qualitative questions which are\r\n			questions which seek a narrative/written response.&nbsp; The short qualitative question type provides a single line text field for respondents\r\n			to enter shorter responses (e.g., their name). The long qualitative\r\n			question type provides multiple lines of text field for respondents to enter\r\n			their responses (e.g., a reflective response).&nbsp; All questions require a\r\n			response when users complete the online form.&nbsp; A response is considered\r\n			something typed into the qualitative box (short or long) or a selection of the\r\n			check box associated with the question.&nbsp; By default, the associated check\r\n			box has the text &quot;<em>I prefer not to answer or not applicable&quot;.&nbsp; </em>This\r\n			response will not be suitable for all situations, so when creating the question\r\n			different text can be selected with the &quot;Add commonly used responses option&quot; or\r\n			simply type in the text you would like to see beside the question\'s check box.\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<br />\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/qualitative%20answers%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"764\" height=\"375\" align=\"right\" />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong>3. Editing a question\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	The <strong>Questions </strong>function in WASSAIL allows users to edit all aspects of existing questions.	\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	a. Open a question for editing: From the <strong>Questions </strong>tab on the WASSAIL main page click on the &quot;edit question&quot; icon.\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/open%20question%20for%20editing%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1002\" height=\"304\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/editing%20questions%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1021\" height=\"388\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	b. When editing is complete click on &quot;Save Question&quot; to either save and close the question or save and continue creating questions.\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/close%20question%20editor%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"774\" height=\"404\" align=\"right\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong>4. Sorting Questions\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	The <strong>Questions </strong>function in WASSAIL allows users to sort all of the existing questions in ascending or descending order numerically by ID#, chronologically by Date Added, and alphabetically by question text. The current sorting format is indicated by the presence of the arrow icon <img src=\"include/helpimages/arrow%20icon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"14\" height=\"18\" />. \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	a. Once a question has been added into WASSAIL, an ID# is automatically generated and assigned to the quesiton. Question ID#\'s can be sorted numerically in ascending or descending order. \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	b. The question text may be sorted alphabetically (by the first letter of the first word in the question) in ascending or descending order.\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	c. Questions can be sorted chronologically by the date the question was added.\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<br />\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/Sorting%20questions%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1107\" height=\"348\" align=\"right\" /><br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium\"><span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong>5. Questions can be filtered by Categories and Tags</strong></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	a.The <strong>Questions </strong>function in WASSAIL allows corresponding <strong>Categories</strong> to be assigned to questions. <strong>Categories</strong> are selected based on the content of the questions. Assigning a <strong>Category</strong> to a question will enable a user to filter a search for all questions containing the same <strong>Category</strong>.\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. Note that this search is case-sensitive.&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/Sort%20by%20category%20-%20W3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1146\" height=\"503\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	b.The <strong>Questions </strong>function in WASAIL allows <strong>Tags</strong> to be created and assigned to questions. Assigning a <strong>Tag</strong> to a question will enable users to filter searches for questions containing the same question <strong>Tag</strong>.\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. Note that the search is case-sensitive.\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/sorting%20by%20Tag%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1147\" height=\"497\" align=\"right\" /><br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong>\r\n5. Printing Questions\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	The <strong>Questions </strong>function in WASSAIL enables the user to print a list of all questions that have been entered into the database. By printing the list of existing questions, the user can easily refer to the questions that have already been entered and avoid entering similar or identical questions into the database.&nbsp; \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	This assists in the repetition of questions in multiple templates. The more a question is asked, the greater the opportunities for data analysis.&nbsp; \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	a. Page setup to print background colours and images: \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. To print WASSAIL screens in full colour (as they appear on the screen) go to &quot;File&quot; on your browser menu and click on &quot;Page Setup&quot;.\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/print%20page%20setup%20-%20FE.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1152\" height=\"448\" align=\"right\" />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/print%20page%20setup%20-%20FE-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"655\" height=\"413\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp; \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;b. Printing questions\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. To print all questions entered into WASSAIL click on the print icon <img src=\"include/helpimages/Print%20page%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"19\" height=\"20\" />&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/print%20page%20-%20W3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"812\" height=\"644\" align=\"right\" />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong>\r\n6. Deleting Questions\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	The <strong>Questions </strong>function in WASSAIL allows users to delete an existing question from the database. A question can only be deleted if it is not currently attached to a questionnaire template. Questions that are attached to a questionnaire template will not have the delete function available.&nbsp; \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	a. In order to delete a question that is attached to a questionnaire template, the question must first be removed from the questionnaire template. Refer to &quot;Templates: Deleting Questions from Templates&quot; for procedures. \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"include/helpimages/deleting questions - FE.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1139\" height=\"612\" align=\"right\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp; \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium\"><strong>7. Displaying Quantitative Question Answers\r\n</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	From the <strong>Questions </strong>tab users can view answers to the listed quantitative questions by clicking on the &quot;Show Answers&quot; <img src=\"include/helpimages/view%20answers.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"23\" height=\"19\" /> icon<img src=\"file:///C:/DOCUME%7E1/wharder/LOCALS%7E1/Temp/moz-screenshot-8.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/Display%20answers%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"852