ire templates. For example, if 10 students have\r\nmanually (on hardcopy) completed the questionnaire for post-test ENG 201 Winter\r\n2010, then 10 separate Questionnaires will have to be manually added in order\r\nto input the students\' responses into WASSAIL. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nResponses may be entered into WASSAIL in two ways:&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Online through a web quesitonnaire</li>\r\n	<li>Manually through WASSAIL </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium\">\r\n1. Entering Responses into a Web Questionnaire\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	a. Enter the Web Questionnaire\'s URL into your web-browser\'s address field.\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		If the &quot;Public&quot; check-box was left blank in the Web Questionnaire editor then it will be necessary to enter one of the computer-generated passwords onto the questionnaire front page. \r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/completing%20web%20questionnaire%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1081\" height=\"672\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</