</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	d. Closing the editor and opening a web questionnaire\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. When the web questionnaire is setup as desired click on <img src=\"include/helpimages/generate%20icon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"92\" height=\"20\" />\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		ii. A popup will display with the web questionnaire URL, as well as questionnaire passwords (if the &quot;Public&quot; check-box was left blank).\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp; <img src=\"include/helpimages/web%20questionnaire%20-%20FE-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1203\" height=\"367\" align=\"right\" />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		iii. <span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium\">Be sure to save the URL and passwords (copy and paste) before closing this popup as it cannot be reopened</span></strong></span>. <br />\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #ff0000\"><br />\r\n	</span>\r\n	<ul>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium\">\r\n8. Accessing web questionnaires \r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<strong>While WASSAIL requires the use of the browser Firefox for setup, web questionnaires can be accessed via any browser. </strong>\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	a.&nbsp;Enter the web questionnaire URL into the address field of the browser navigation bar. The loading page of the web questionnaire will display. \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	b. Click <img src=\"include/helpimages/begin%20icon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"17\" /> to open the questionnaire. \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/web%20questionnaire%20-%20FE-6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1172\" height=\"489\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n'),('/reports.php','<p>\r\nThe <strong>Reports </strong>function in WASSAIL allows for the compilation of individual responses into meaningful summaries. For example, a report could provide a snapshot of how students in a particular class, a particular academic year, and/or a particular discipline performed on their pre-tests, post-tests or one-shots, etc. This allows instructors or administrators to tailor Information Literacy course content to address the strengths or weaknesses or a particular group of students, as well as providing evidence of student progress and learning. WASSAIL also allows users to limit results by year of study, gender, or other particular demographic responses to the questions administered, as long as the demographic questions are asked. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium\">\r\n1. Generate a report\r\n</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	To begin, from the WASSAIL main page select the <strong>Reports </strong>tab \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/reports%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1074\" height=\"222\" align=\"right\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p align=\"left\">\r\n	a. From the <strong>Reports</strong> tab select the desired Template(s), Course, Year(s), Term(s) and Type(s) of questions/responses that are to be viewed.&nbsp;With each box, multiple items can be selected by holding the &quot;Shift&quot; key. \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<strong>For this example&nbsp; we selected:&nbsp; </strong>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p align=\"left\">\r\n	Template: Test Template 1\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p align=\"left\">\r\n	Course: ENG201 \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p align=\"left\">\r\n	Year: 2010-2011 \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p align=\"left\">\r\n	Term: Spring \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p align=\"left\">\r\n	Type: Pre-test \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/generating%20reports%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"811\" height=\"501\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<p>\r\n		&nbsp;i. Selecting &quot;Any&quot; will provide results for all courses and years available for the selected template(s).\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n		&nbsp;ii. Results will be grouped by template questions and will not be differentiated by course or year if multiple courses or years are selected. \r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	b. Selecting responses to view:\r\n	</p>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<p>\r\n		i. The screen shot below shows how the user can define the report to be displayed. Click on &quot;Show questions&quot; to see the results for the selected parameters.&nbsp;\r\n		</p>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			<p>\r\n			1. To run a report to see all results for all questions, check <strong>Show \r\n			All </strong>(e.g., see section 1.b.ii.1.a below).\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n			&nbsp;\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n			2. To run a report listing the results for all questions, but limited by specific criteria (i.e. age = 18-21), check <strong>Show All</strong>, and then select the appropriate check-box under Answers for the limiting criteria that you wish the report to display. In this example, the data in the report reflects responses provided by any respondents who selected the answer, &quot;age = 18-21&quot; (e.g., see section1.b.ii.3.a below). \r\n			</p>\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			<p>\r\n			3. To run a report listing all results for one particular or a limited \r\n			number of questions, leave <strong>Show All</strong> blank and select the \r\n			appropriate check-boxes for the results that you wish to display on \r\n			the report\r\n			(e.g., see section1.b.ii.2.a below).\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n			&nbsp;\r\n			</p>\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n		<p>\r\n		Note: When leaving <strong>Show All</strong> unchecked, there must be at least one\r\n		or more questions selected under <strong>Answers</strong>. If no questions are \r\n		selected an error message will display stating &quot;You must select at least\r\n		one question on which to report&quot;. \r\n		</p>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/gen%20report%20-%20W3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1108\" height=\"714\" align=\"right\" /> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp; \r\n	</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	c. Sample Quantitative Reports \r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		i. Where &quot;Show All&quot; is selected: \r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<blockquote>\r\n		<blockquote>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana; color: black\">1. This\r\n			report is run without limiters and therefore displays results provided by all\r\n			respondents to all questions (graphic below displays a portion of the report).</span> <br />\r\n		</blockquote>\r\n	</blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<img src=\"include/helpimages/gen%20report%20-%20W3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1091\" height=\"454\" align=\"right\" />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n	</p>